Nicola McLean's husband Tom Williams has hinted he'll be heading into the Celebrity Big Brother house. 
On Thursday evening, the 36-year-old footballer tweeted a pal saying: "Bro these housemates aren't ready for me #notonmylevel." 
While a source told the Daily Star earlier in the week that he was "trying to convince" show bosses to let him go into the Hertfordshire house during Friday's eviction. 
It comes as Nicola, who shares two sons with Tom, and Jamie O'Hara were blasted by fans of the show. 
The pair have been flirting relentlessly throughout the series despite the fact that she is married to footballer Tom Williams. 
And on Thursday evening the two appeared even closer when he gave her a neck massage. 
Viewers tuning in at home were not impressed with the scenes and slammed them on Twitter afterwards.
